item.description:

[quote=“Ruby, post:10, topic:454359”][quote author=t3z2a link=topic=557226.msg4100139#msg4100139 date=1347345374]

To do this open any other mod icon in photoshop,
then go to image>adjustments>Hue/Saturation,

Click colorize then move the slider to the pink etc,
save as "Pinkmod.png"etc,
And your all done.
